Source: plot-script
Section: scientific
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Artur Glavic <artur.glavic@gmail.com>
Standards-Version: 3.8.1
Homepage: http://plotpy.sourceforge.net/plotwiki/

Package: plot-script
Architecture: all
Depends: python (>= 2.4), gnuplot (>= 4.2), python-numpy (>= 1.0), python-scipy (>= 0.7), python-gtk2 (>= 2.0), python-gobject (>= 2.0), python-imaging, ipython, gfortran, gcc
Description: Program to plot measured data with Gnuplot. Provides a GUI interface, fitting and some other useful functionalities. Supported file types are 4circle (.spec)/MPMS,PPMS (.dat/.raw)/reflectometer (.UXD)/TREFF/IN12/DNS and can be widened with plugins.

